        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-08-03T19:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-08-03T19:00:00-05:00" n="954" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d954">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 Control (Italy)/8–145: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in Italy</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Kirk</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-08-03T20:00:00-04:00">August 3, 1945—8 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1303. Urtel 2158, July 31. If it is decided that military considerations require
                    maintenance of AMG in Udine Province until December 1, Ital Govt should be
                    informed and public announcement made of reasons therefor.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
